'''Green Squad''' was the name given to all training squads in [[Alliance Training Center-5/Green Squad]] before they received their own designation. One particular group, which went on to become [[Green Squad 3]], was in the middle of its final training exercise and had just received the [[Datafile/Legends|data file]] [[Green3]] when [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces attacked the base. They helped fight off the forces by entering the mobile command base and destroying it from the inside.

